A great majority of juggernauts are actually weak though. there are a few outliers that have found strength, but not most of them. Here is a list actually.

Weak Juggers:{{champion:86}} {{champion:420}} {{champion:82}} {{champion:75}} {{champion:102}} {{champion:48}} {{champion:77}} {{champion:106}} {{champion:36}} 

Strong Juggers:{{champion:83}} {{champion:122}} 

(these are based on popularity to winrate)

 also juggernauts tend to ignore cc pretty well. This is because a lot of them have abilities that work through cc (such as garen's spin, trundle's ult, olaf's ult) and a lot of them also build pretty tanky, so they can absorb more damage while cc'd.
